column5: A friend of mine is planning a trip there labour day, would like me to come. Anyone know how fishing is up there or which rivers or lakes to target for good fishing?
Its a reallybig area can you be more specific or tell us what you would like to target. Boat or no boat?

I think he is aiming for north end closer to manatoulin island.  Would like to rent boat, Also shore fish and wading. Different things different days. Lake and river.  He's planning to set up at a camp ground.

Cyprus Lake National Park. Camping, canoe rentals, Smallmouth and walleye in the lake. But if you don't have a reservation yet you might not get in. Its very popular due to the spectacular swimming and cliff jumping on georgian bay at the park.
